		<title>How are you connected to 48Days?</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/48Days/~3/xWlsGJguspw/</link>
		<comments>http://www.48days.com/2011/06/15/how-are-you-connected-to-48days/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 15 Jun 2011 08:00:30 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Dan Miller</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.48days.com/?p=7278</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[I appreciate your connection to the 48Days community.  Every now and then we like to give you some new<a href="http://www.48days.com/reader-survey/"></a> options and to get feedback on your preferences.
There are many ways to get the 48 Days Blog daily or weekly newsletter!  You can subscribe via RSS <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/48Days">HERE</a> or get the blog in your email inbox <a href="http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=nomoremondaysblog&#38;loc=en_US">HERE</a>. (we&#8230; <a href="http://www.48days.com/2011/06/15/how-are-you-connected-to-48days/" class="read_more">More...</a>]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I appreciate your connection to the 48Days community.  Every now and then we like to give you some new<a href="http://www.48days.com/reader-survey/"><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-7279" title="survey" src="http://www.48days.com/wp-content/uploads/survey.png" alt="" width="248" height="168" /></a> options and to get feedback on your preferences.</p>
<p>There are many ways to get the 48 Days Blog daily or weekly newsletter!  You can subscribe via RSS <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/48Days">HERE</a> or get the blog in your email inbox <a href="http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=nomoremondaysblog&amp;loc=en_US">HERE</a>. (we promise we keep your email private)</p>
<p>Twitter is another way to get both the blog and FaceBook updates.  Just follow <a href="http://twitter.com/#%21/48DaysTeam">@48DaysTeam</a>.</p>
<p>The FaceBook fan page is another resource to connect and comment on daily updates: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Dan-Miller-Career-Coach-Author-of-48-Days-to-the-Work-You-Love/147834932132?ref=ts">48 Days FaceBook Page</a></p>
<p>Additionally, there is the weekly <a href="http://www.48days.com/listen/">Podcast</a> (also in <a href="http://itunes.apple.com/podcast/48-days-to-the-work-you-love/id178145160">iTunes</a>), the 48 Days weekly <a href="http://www.48days.com/48-days-newsletter/sign-up/">Newsletter</a>, and of course, the <a href="http://www.48days.net">48 Days Community</a>.</p>
<p>What are you doing to stay connected?  <a href="http://www.48days.com/reader-survey/">Take our survey</a> and let us know.  (Bonus for you &#8211; a free eBook when you finish the survey).</p>
