		<item>
		<title>The little difference………..</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/48Days/~3/7yh2udxMwOw/</link>
		<comments>http://www.48days.com/2011/06/10/the-little-difference/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Fri, 10 Jun 2011 08:00:30 +0000</pubDate>

		<dc:creator>Dan Miller</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[No More Mondays]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[difference]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Longfellow]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.48days.com/?p=7203</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<em><strong>“The Heights of great men gained and kept are not achieved by sudden flight. But they, while their companions slept, toiled upward through the night.”</strong></em> Henry Wadsworth Longfellow
It’s the little things that make a difference.  Spending just 48 minutes a day for 48 days can change the direction of your life.  You can find a new job, start&#8230; <a href="http://www.48days.com/2011/06/10/the-little-difference/" class="read_more">More...</a>]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>
<p><em><strong>“The Heights of great men gained and kept are not achieved by sudden flight. But they, while their companions slept, toiled upward through the night.”</strong></em> Henry Wadsworth Longfellow</p>
<p>It’s the little things that make a difference.  Spending just 48 minutes a day for 48 days can change the direction of your life.  You can find a new job, start a new business, create healing in negative relationships, or correct your eating habits for transformed health and begin the rest of your life with higher levels of success than experienced by 98% of the general population.</p>
</div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
