		<title>Try following what “amuses your mind”</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/48Days/~3/T4qEKFhpw88/</link>
		<comments>http://www.48days.com/2011/05/25/try-following-what-%e2%80%9camuses-your-mind%e2%80%9d/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 25 May 2011 08:00:54 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Dan Miller</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Finding Passion]]></category>

		<category><![CDATA[jared angaza]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[karmann ghia]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[oprah]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Plato]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[what amuses your mind]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.48days.com/?p=7058</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[“Do not then train youth to learn by force and harshness; but direct them to it by what amuses their minds so that you may be better able to discover with accuracy the peculiar bent of the genius of each.&#8221;  &#8212; Plato
My son <a href="http://jaredangaza.com/">Jared</a> failed miserably in the public school classroom.  We removed him from that “harsh” environment<a&#8230; <a href="http://www.48days.com/2011/05/25/try-following-what-%e2%80%9camuses-your-mind%e2%80%9d/" class="read_more">More...</a>]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>“Do not then train youth to learn by force and harshness; but direct them to it by what amuses their minds so that you may be better able to discover with accuracy the peculiar bent of the genius of each.&#8221;  &#8212; Plato</p>
<p>My son <a href="http://jaredangaza.com/">Jared</a> failed miserably in the public school classroom.  We removed him from that “harsh” environment<a rel="attachment wp-att-7059" href="http://www.48days.com/2011/05/25/try-following-what-%e2%80%9camuses-your-mind%e2%80%9d/karmann-ghia/"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-7059" title="karmann-ghia" src="http://www.48days.com/wp-content/uploads/karmann-ghia-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" /></a> where they demanded that he know physics and mathematics from a book – to be well rounded and “educated.”  When he was fourteen I bought a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Volkswagen_Karmann_Ghia">1968 VW Karmann Ghia</a> for Jared’s first car.  Together we sanded the body and ultimately painted it ourselves – Porsche Guards Red.  We replaced the interior carpeting, all the rubber around the glass and most of the exterior chrome.  We pulled the engine and supertuned it from top to bottom.  Jared learned about electrical systems, internal combustion, brake systems – and oh yes, physics and mathematics in the process.  The resulting eye-popping ride was a source of pride and knowledge for Jared because it was also a focus for his pleasure.  And it gave him <a href="http://jaredangaza.com/">the framework for helping others</a> find unique expressions of their God-given talents.</p>
<p>Bill Gates, Michael Dell, Oprah Winfrey, Michelangelo, Henry David Thoreau, Angelina Jolie, Donald Trump, Justin Bieber, and Mr. Rogers all seemed to have developed what amused their minds.</p>
<p>Are you trying to grow by submitting yourself to “force and harshness” or are you paying attention to “what amuses your mind?”  Have you bought into the common philosophy that if you enjoy something you certainly can’t make a living with that as a focus?  Why don’t you stop beating yourself up and just follow your passions?   You just might go directly toward success.</p>
<p>In <strong><em><a href="http://www.48days.com/store/learn-and-grow-rich/">Learn &amp; Grow Rich</a></em></strong> I’ve identified the books, seminars, blogs and other resources that can make your learning change who you are and put money in your bank account – beginning immediately.</p>
<div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/48Days?a=T4qEKFhpw88:s-xuITWtNA0:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/48Days?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/48Days?a=T4qEKFhpw88:s-xuITWtNA0:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/48Days?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/48Days?a=T4qEKFhpw88:s-xuITWtNA0:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/48Days?i=T4qEKFhpw88:s-xuITWtNA0:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/48Days?a=T4qEKFhpw88:s-xuITWtNA0:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/48Days?i=T4qEKFhpw88:s-xuITWtNA0:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a>
