		<item>
		<title>Yes, it’s true…</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/48Days/~3/Bk4wglCjD0s/</link>
		<comments>http://www.48days.com/2011/05/20/yes-it%e2%80%99s-true%e2%80%a6/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Fri, 20 May 2011 08:00:54 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Dan Miller</dc:creator>

				<category><![CDATA[Workplace Humor]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[bonus]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[new job]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[pay raise]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.48days.com/?p=6975</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[&#8220;I have to have a raise,&#8221; Eric said to his boss. &#8220;And I probably should let you know, there are three other companies after me.&#8221;
&#8220;Is that so?&#8221; asked the manager. &#8220;And just who are those other companies that are after you?&#8221;
&#8220;The electric company, the telephone company, and the gas company.&#8221;
&#160;
]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>&#8220;I have to have a raise,&#8221; Eric said to his boss. &#8220;And I probably should let you know, there are three other companies after me.&#8221;</p>
<p>&#8220;Is that so?&#8221; asked the manager. &#8220;And just who are those other companies that are after you?&#8221;</p>
<p>&#8220;The electric company, the telephone company, and the gas company.&#8221;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div class="feedflare">
